1|GAME4|1|This exercise will test your chef's ability to sort ingredients.
2|GAME4|2| At the top are six ingredients, with their equivalents at the bottom.
3|GAME4|3| Only thing is, the ingredients are jumbled!
4|GAME4|4| An arrow at the top will highlight the first ingredient to be sorted.
5|GAME4|5| You have to find that ingredient at the bottom of the screen and click on it.
6|GAME4|6| Then the arrow will highlight the next ingredient to be sorted, and so forth, until your chef has sorted all the ingredients.
7|GAME4|7|Sort all the ingredients before the timer reaches zero, and your chef's ingredient rating will improve!
8|CCCKSIN|1|Stocked Ingredients
9|CCCKSIN|2|Left-click to view a list of ingredients that the competing chef can use to prepare the selected recipe for this round.
10|RECIPEIN|1|Requires: %1s
11|GAME5|1|This is an exercise to test your cooking efficiency while under pressure.
12|GAME5|2| All sorts of ingredients will start falling, and your chef has to pick up every ingredient with the plate before they fall on the ground.
13|GAME5|3|The more ingredients you manage to pick up, the more efficient and faster your chef will be at preparing food, allowing more time to perfect the recipes!
